            Clause 22 [<span class="italic">Period of effect etc of freezing order</span>]:</p><p>
            [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 71 not moved.</span>]
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_191gc' title='Col. 191GC &mdash; HL Deb 08 July 2004 vol 663 c191GC' name='column_191gc' href='#column_191gc' rel='bookmark'>191GC</a>
            Clause 22 agreed to.</p><p>
