        <a name='S5LV0663P0_20040708_GCR2_234'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-charles-lyell' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0663P0_20040708_GCR2_234' title='Link to this speech by Mr Charles Lyell' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-charles-lyell" title="Mr Charles Lyell">The Deputy Speaker (Lord Lyell)</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The Committee stands adjourned until Tuesday at 3.30 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0663P0_20040708_GCR2_235' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at five minutes past seven o'clock.
      </p>
